      <title>继上周下跌后，中国开始抑制人民币贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-maintains-grip-on-yuan-with-fix-stronger-than-7-2-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周人民币下跌引发市场猜测，认为决策者将允许人民币更快贬值。此后，中国重申了对人民币的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-maintains-grip-on-yuan-with-fix-stronger-than-7-2-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
