      <title>美联储官员表达通胀担忧后黄金延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/gold-holds-decline-after-fed-officials-express-inflation-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储官员周末的言论强化了人们的观点，即美国央行将在 2025 年采取更为谨慎的降息态度，黄金价格连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/gold-holds-decline-after-fed-officials-express-inflation-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 00:30:48 GMT</pubDate>
